    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167360/extras/5e840a9e1372c8227fbe47a0633a6322.avif?t=1770865080\" width=835 height=243 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>如果所有的玩具都有灵魂？</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个世界里，被珍惜的玩具会萌生自我，获得自由行动的能力。然而，一旦被抛弃，它们的心就会破碎，变成袭击他人的怪物。玩具们既懂得被爱的喜悦，也深知被遗弃的绝望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167360/extras/3ac09bdd57b77cbc7f1e32d09c9f2863.avif?t=1770865080\" width=925 height=173 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>被遗弃的人偶“莉莉”的孤独旅程</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了再次回到主人身边，主角莉莉开始了奔跑。身后是失去了自我、巨大的玩具怪物。一旦被抓住，就意味着结束。请利用娇小的身体，从绝望的追逐中逃脱吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167360/extras/bac1d8c5e7fedd9fae554864f3f1a795.avif?t=1770865080\" width=929 height=274 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>直观的操作，穿越噩梦</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作支持手柄和键盘操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式3D横向卷轴</strong>：由UE5打造，讲究景深与光影的诡异世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>躲藏、跳跃、逃跑</strong>：仔细观察周围和敌人，开辟前进的道路。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>浓缩的恐怖体验</strong>：在相当于一部电影时长的游戏时间内，凝缩了极致的紧张感与故事。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167360/extras/cabe06f689856943b9542f893679e8f2.avif?t=1770865080\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p>",
